<h2 class="bold font-l">Weekend at Bernie's II</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The film starts off with credits displayed alongside a short animation depicting what happened before the film's events. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnimatedCreditsOpening" class='trope-example-link'>Animated Credits Opening</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
